text.tspan: Step one – measure
At Eternity we present your biomarkers and health indicators arranged using the INTEGRAL acronym – so as to emphasize
the importance of a comprehensive lifestyle program to enhance your health and longevity. Details of all your results and
your programs are monitored on your personal Lifetime Health Assessment and Monitoring Program (LHAMP).
Step two – mentor
At Eternity our focus is on reversing cardiometabolic disease, which is the key to successful Age Management. Our Physicians
and Lifestyle coaches will help you improve those key lifestyle factors known to inﬂuence your gene expression and slow
down the aging process.
Getting and keeping your biomarkers in the e-zone (optimum health zone) is key– only by repeated measuring a
nd
monitoring utilizing your personal LHAMP can we be sure your integral health program is working. Our initial goal will focus
on correcting the worst 3 scores in each of the 8-lifestyle modules.
Step three – monitor (e-LHAMP)
This is perhaps the most unique and exciting feature of Eternity. We use state of the art screening and digital devices tailored
to your genetic individuality to monitor all your health data on your personal (e-LHAMP). All your health indicators can
be instantly displayed on your computer or phone 24/7 365 days a year. This helps keep all key biomarkers in the e-zone
(optimum zone) and shows that your Age Management program is efective.
Using the Eternity “3m solution” of Mea
suring, Mentoring and Monitoring enables positive lifestyle change that will quickly
optimize your health.
